quran[4{c,v,t}:
2,102,"aur un ( hazliyaat ) ke peechay lag gay jo Sulaiman ke ahdِ saltanat mein shyatin parha karte they aur Sulaiman ne mutlaq kufar ki baat nahi ki, balkay shetan hi kufar karte they ke logon ko jaadoo sikhate they. aur un baton ke bhi ( peechay lag gay ) jo shehar babul mein do firshton ( yani ) harwat aur Maruat par utri theen. aur woh dono kisi ko kuch nahi sikhate they, jab taq yeh nah keh dete ke hum to (zaryaٴ ) azmaish hain. tum kufar mein nah parro. gharz log un se ( aisa ) jaadoo sikhte, jis se miyan biwi mein judai daal den. aur khuda ke hukum ke siwa woh is ( jaadoo ) se kisi ka kuch bhi nahi bigaar satke they. aur kuch aisay ( mantar ) sikhte jo un ko nuqsaan hi pohanchate aur faida kuch nah dete. aur woh jantay they ke jo shakhs aisi cheezon ( yani sehar aur mantar waghera ) ka khredar hoga, is ka akhirat mein kuch hissa nahi. aur jis cheez ke aiwz unhon ne apni jaanun ko beech dala, woh buri thi. kash woh ( is baat ko ) jantay"
2,103,"aur agar woh imaan laatay aur parhaiz gari karte to khuda ke haan se bohat acha sila milta. ae kash, woh is se waaqif hotay"
2,104,"ae ahal imaan! ( guftagu ke waqt pighmbrِ khuda se ) ra-ana nah kaha karo. anzarna kaha karo. aur khoob sun rakho, aur kafiroon ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab hai"
2,105,"jo log kafir hain, ahal kitaab ya mushriq woh is baat ko pasand nahi karte ke tum par tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se kher ( wa barkat ) nazil ho. aur khuda to jis ko chahta hai, apni rehmat ke sath khaas kar laita hai aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai"
